Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.34,0:01:33.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克洛斯王国？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.07,0:01:38.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是这个大陆的中心 很热闹对不对
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.78,0:01:39.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和阿利亚差多了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.46,0:01:42.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…克劳德 你看
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.20,0:01:44.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可爱哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.93,0:01:45.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.65,0:01:50.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 现在不是做这种事情的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.29,0:01:59.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见了 蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.46,0:02:01.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此唐突地前来拜访
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.16,0:02:03.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还能得到您的接见
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.01,0:02:05.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是由衷的感谢您
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.95,0:02:06.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,国王陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.80,0:02:09.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷吉斯还好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.50,0:02:10.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.78,0:02:13.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他还是那么顽固吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.10,0:02:14.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.43,0:02:16.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.45,0:02:18.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.81,0:02:21.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说你叫克劳德是吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.88,0:02:22.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是、是的 陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.96,0:02:26.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想调查索沙陨石是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.60,0:02:26.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.93,0:02:30.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,索沙陨石所在的艾尔大陆
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.76,0:02:34.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受其影响所产生的魔物们\N目前还处于和人们交战的状态
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.55,0:02:37.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然还没有战况传来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.53,0:02:40.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过胜利的话应该就会有所传闻
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.97,0:02:44.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我国派出的特使至今也还没有回来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.99,0:02:47.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可能会是一趟赌上性命的旅途
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.52,0:02:48.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此你也还是要去吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.77,0:02:50.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.99,0:02:52.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜也是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.16,0:02:54.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.78,0:02:55.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再问你们一次
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.32,0:02:57.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们可不要后悔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.71,0:02:58.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.59,0:03:07.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通行证你们拿去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.94,0:03:14.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是到艾尔大陆的通行证啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.76,0:03:18.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,往来大陆之间居然需要通行证
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.08,0:03:19.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一点都不知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.27,0:03:23.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.05,0:03:26.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是没有你的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.56,0:03:28.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想可能就拿不到这张通行证呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.92,0:03:31.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这都是你的功劳哟 蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.88,0:03:32.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别…别这么说…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.61,0:03:35.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这点事没什么好谢的啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.52,0:03:40.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过真的好紧张哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.74,0:03:43.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然国王的那种威严好庄严啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.35,0:03:47.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你给我识相点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.47,0:03:50.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看该识相点的人应该是你们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.69,0:03:51.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.23,0:03:54.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太缠人的男人可不受欢迎哟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.53,0:03:55.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.63,0:03:57.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要以为你是女人我们才来陪你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.02,0:04:01.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们可是听说你要找保镖才来找你的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.25,0:04:04.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说 我不是拒绝了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.96,0:04:07.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事哪是你说了就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.54,0:04:08.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总要把理由说清楚…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.31,0:04:09.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长得太丑了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.48,0:04:10.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么！？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.79,0:04:15.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你们三个并不是我喜欢的类型啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.41,0:04:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说 你们还是算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.94,0:04:20.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思咯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.52,0:04:22.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.18,0:04:22.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.87,0:04:24.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自以为是女人就…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.28,0:04:27.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.12,0:04:27.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.24,0:04:29.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是什么人？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.50,0:04:32.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三大男人欺负一个女人太卑鄙了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.29,0:04:32.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.55,0:04:36.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小兄弟 想打架吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.62,0:04:48.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你在干什么啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.53,0:04:49.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 有没有听见啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.85,0:04:52.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决定了！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.16,0:04:55.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我决定选你当我的保镖
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.03,0:04:56.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.62,0:04:58.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.08,0:05:00.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.31,0:05:03.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们几个…我们的话可还没说完呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.64,0:05:07.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要用你的脏手碰我！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.91,0:05:13.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是敢碰我的身体 就得有相当的觉悟的哟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.78,0:05:21.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以为你是谁啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.85,0:05:22.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…危险！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.32,0:05:25.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.76,0:05:33.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论如何都要做个了断了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.52,0:05:36.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位 很危险哟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.99,0:05:38.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家退后一点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.30,0:05:41.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不会再手下留情了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.72,0:05:43.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看我们怎么修理你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.01,0:05:49.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.81,0:05:50.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙…难道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.32,0:05:51.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.96,0:05:54.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沉睡于吾体内的红莲之火啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.49,0:05:56.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奉火界王派蒙之名
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.34,0:05:58.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此解放汝等
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.30,0:06:01.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在圣三角的引导下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.82,0:06:03.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将阻挡在吾面前者
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.48,0:06:04.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给予灼热的制裁！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.72,0:06:12.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,焰之矢！(Fire Bolt)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.27,0:06:20.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 搞定
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.05,0:06:25.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫塞丽奴•茱莉丝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.29,0:06:26.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.02,0:06:29.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我叫做克劳德……
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.45,0:06:31.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克劳德 那我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.07,0:06:34.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,え什么啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.74,0:06:36.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已经是我的保镖了哟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.43,0:06:38.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那、那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.46,0:06:40.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.55,0:06:52.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克洛斯洞窟马上就要到了哟 克劳德
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.04,0:06:53.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…这样啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.55,0:06:57.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克劳德在搞什么嘛 还会不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.18,0:07:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来和我们的目的地完全不一样嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.25,0:07:03.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克洛斯的秘宝到底是什么样的宝藏呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.32,0:07:05.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心里好兴奋哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.64,0:07:08.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宝藏猎人啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.56,0:07:10.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还是一流的哟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.62,0:07:12.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的招术呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.90,0:07:15.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 你不知道 纹章术 吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.19,0:07:17.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纹章术？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.85,0:07:21.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用刻画在身上某种特定形状的纹章
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.75,0:07:26.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将念力转换成各种不同形态的能量
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.82,0:07:28.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大致上来说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.20,0:07:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分为空气 水 火 地 等图形
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.68,0:07:33.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将天魔之名作为烙印
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.31,0:07:36.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能作为 纹章术 使用了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.03,0:07:41.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿我来说 像我刚才使用火系法术的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.39,0:07:45.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是利用掌管 火 的三角形的纹章
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.21,0:07:47.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三角形的纹章…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.18,0:07:50.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 浮现在这里哟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.22,0:07:54.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞丽奴小姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.73,0:07:57.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀…我好象没有要你一起跟过来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.26,0:07:59.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞丽奴小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.68,0:08:01.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么需要克劳德呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.60,0:08:04.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是说过让他做我的保镖吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.17,0:08:05.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.36,0:08:08.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够使用那种纹章术的纹章术师
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.01,0:08:11.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好象不需要什么保镖的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.48,0:08:13.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们回去吧 克劳德
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.13,0:08:16.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的目的又不是宝藏
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.88,0:08:18.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是索沙陨石才对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.76,0:08:19.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩……
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.66,0:08:22.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,索沙陨石…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.21,0:08:25.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然这是我听来的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.54,0:08:29.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说克洛斯洞窟由于索沙陨石的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.60,0:08:32.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好象受到影响什么来着…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.75,0:08:35.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受到索沙陨石的影响？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.31,0:08:37.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的吗 塞丽奴小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.23,0:08:40.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人的 我没听过这样的说法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.77,0:08:43.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也只能怪你的消息不够灵通咯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.56,0:08:46.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到镇上问问看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.93,0:08:48.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.53,0:08:52.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么现在就去确认一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.93,0:08:56.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实根本就没这回事哟^^
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.12,0:08:57.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那好 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.14,0:08:58.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克劳德
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.80,0:09:02.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是真的到了那里就清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.74,0:09:03.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是……
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.44,0:09:04.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经有白跑一趟的心理准备了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.19,0:09:07.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总比没去 事后后悔要来的好得多
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.71,0:09:10.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然克劳德你都这么说了……
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.97,0:09:11.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.95,0:09:12.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.84,0:09:14.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们就往克洛斯洞窟前进吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.05,0:09:25.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比想象中的还要大哎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.12,0:09:28.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到处都是湿湿的…感觉很不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.20,0:09:33.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 这么快就有岔路了啊……
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.08,0:09:35.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走哪一边呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.15,0:09:36.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看地图吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.15,0:09:39.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么黑看不到哎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.36,0:09:42.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要我去弄点火照亮？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.58,0:09:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 没有那个必要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.27,0:09:48.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在混浊之泉沐浴的明界王拉格苏醒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.06,0:09:52.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是纹章术师
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.26,0:09:54.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.92,0:09:58.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问 ……这张是藏宝图吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.37,0:09:58.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.29,0:10:00.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这张是真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.18,0:10:02.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太没礼貌了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.48,0:10:06.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我在克洛斯王国最大的拍卖会上\N好不容易竞标得来的真品哟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.08,0:10:09.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还附有鉴定书呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.96,0:10:13.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藏宝图居然会有坚定书 这不是很可疑吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.45,0:10:14.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴 走左边这条路
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.78,0:10:17.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是受不了现在的年轻人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.51,0:10:19.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点跟上来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.44,0:10:25.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还好吧 蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.76,0:10:30.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也太没用了吧 只不过是蝙蝠而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.76,0:10:34.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 这是人家第一次看到蝙蝠…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.00,0:10:38.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.92,0:10:41.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.20,0:10:44.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.30,0:10:54.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说塞丽奴小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.07,0:10:55.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个地方真的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.35,0:10:59.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么东西受到了索沙陨石的影响吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.21,0:11:06.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯…真的有…真的有的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.81,0:11:12.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.80,0:11:13.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.67,0:11:15.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.44,0:11:17.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你如果还不能走路就再休息一会儿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.90,0:11:20.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的没有事了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.45,0:11:23.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好  年轻就是好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.67,0:11:25.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过麻烦你们走快一点好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.33,0:11:30.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀？这还真是怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.39,0:11:32.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又没路了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.12,0:11:35.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这已经是第七次了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.30,0:11:38.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是一直照着地图走吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.80,0:11:42.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地图上画的还有路可走的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.44,0:11:45.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这地图果然是假货嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.49,0:11:48.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们回头吧 快
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.94,0:11:51.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你惹她生气了哎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.73,0:12:09.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞丽奴小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.69,0:12:12.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀……讨厌虫子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.09,0:12:18.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌虫子啦 讨厌讨厌……
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.43,0:12:18.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等等 塞丽奴小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.83,0:12:21.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是她要雇佣保镖的理由啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.33,0:12:24.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 塞丽奴小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.26,0:12:25.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把虫子丢掉了哟
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.00,0:12:27.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经没事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.16,0:12:29.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真…真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.00,0:12:31.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她这个人还真可爱…呃！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.77,0:12:34.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊　吓死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.84,0:12:36.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.50,0:12:42.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的…人家吓得心跳得好快哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.81,0:12:43.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摸摸看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.76,0:12:46.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞利奴…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.16,0:12:50.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么声音！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.63,0:12:52.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么东西…过来了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.13,0:13:12.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虫…虫…虫子！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.46,0:13:13.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大一条！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.07,0:13:21.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.88,0:13:30.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 这是什么跟什么啊 真是受不了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.83,0:13:32.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总算是逃出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.49,0:13:37.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子好饿哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.81,0:13:39.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这人还真诚实啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.68,0:13:41.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过肚子还真是饿了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.43,0:13:43.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.69,0:13:45.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些饼干如果可以的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.67,0:13:47.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊　谢…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.48,0:13:49.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就不客气咯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.90,0:13:55.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然有一点受潮 但是这个时候就凑合着吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.39,0:13:59.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞丽奴小姐 这些饼干是为了克劳德…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.69,0:14:01.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了　我吃饱了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.70,0:14:03.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的你们两个就分着吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.63,0:14:05.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只剩下一块了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.13,0:14:08.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请拿去吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.83,0:14:10.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正我肚子还不饿
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.91,0:14:12.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.86,0:14:14.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一人一半
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.25,0:14:16.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃？　克劳德…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.45,0:14:22.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀　还挺亲热的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.80,0:14:24.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞…塞丽奴小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.64,0:14:26.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在胡说什么啊 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.18,0:14:29.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是叫人羡慕啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.84,0:14:33.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当个一流的宝藏猎人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.61,0:14:35.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全没有谈恋爱得空闲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.82,0:14:37.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这是在炫耀？还是在埋怨？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.17,0:14:40.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那张地图一定是假的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.63,0:14:42.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.11,0:14:45.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可知道我花了多少钱才买到它的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.91,0:14:46.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的……
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.74,0:14:48.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…刚才的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.86,0:14:53.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞丽奴小姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.26,0:14:55.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.94,0:14:58.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家的胸部会被磨小的啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.39,0:15:04.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛痛痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.76,0:15:07.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这算是什么啊　真是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.29,0:15:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦　这里是？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.78,0:15:21.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是歪打正着　运气真不错
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.62,0:15:31.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神殿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.02,0:15:34.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这应该是旧文明的遗址吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.43,0:15:38.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来我们好象被塞丽奴小姐给唬弄了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.74,0:15:44.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里根本没有什么跟索沙陨石有关的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.55,0:15:46.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的　果然塞丽奴她…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.19,0:15:49.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃？话说回来塞丽奴小姐呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.11,0:15:50.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.97,0:15:54.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边这边　你们俩快点过来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.88,0:16:08.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.24,0:16:10.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克洛斯的秘宝？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.03,0:16:12.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宝藏发现了哟
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.47,0:16:18.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里装了什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.52,0:16:21.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀？你不是没感兴趣吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.89,0:16:35.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危险！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.52,0:16:43.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么石像…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.69,0:16:49.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说是索沙陨石的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.87,0:16:50.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.17,0:16:53.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些石像上附着守护灵
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.91,0:16:55.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,守护灵？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.75,0:16:58.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前曾经听说过
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.91,0:16:59.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在旧文明时代
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.13,0:17:01.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宫廷的纹章术师
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.08,0:17:02.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了守护
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.31,0:17:05.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便让灵魂附着在武器或者是石像上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.24,0:17:12.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.74,0:17:28.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 居然弹开了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.56,0:17:33.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火焰矢！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.11,0:17:39.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧 蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.02,0:17:40.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞丽奴小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.96,0:17:41.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.96,0:17:49.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它根本就毫发无伤嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.86,0:17:51.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎么样才能打倒它们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.92,0:17:52.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克劳德
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.76,0:17:54.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是一会儿也好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.02,0:17:57.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能帮我暂时缠住他们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.02,0:18:00.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想试试一个纹章术
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.58,0:18:04.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 这个咒文的咒语很长
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.66,0:18:07.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是在咒语咏唱的途中被他们打断的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.62,0:18:08.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咒文就无法完成
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.66,0:18:10.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 我懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.69,0:18:14.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪物们　宝藏在这里！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.02,0:18:18.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在赤圣三角的引导下 控制火的火界王派蒙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.13,0:18:22.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在银新月的引导下 控制水的水界王亚里顿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.62,0:18:27.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在金正方的引导下 控制地的地界王阿迈蒙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.44,0:18:32.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在青圆的引导下　控制月的空气界王奥里姆斯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.92,0:18:36.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在支配自然界的汝等之佑护下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.22,0:18:39.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引导这蓝锥圆
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.10,0:18:46.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昭示天地四方 古往今来的真理
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.83,0:18:49.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拥抱吾等的四方境界
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.34,0:18:52.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掌管万物的星辰
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.99,0:18:52.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没完吗　塞丽奴？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.25,0:18:54.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞利奴　快点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.78,0:18:55.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以照耀四方的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.30,0:18:59.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赐予吾等白术之光吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.18,0:18:56.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.81,0:19:05.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,零！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.19,0:19:25.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.03,0:19:30.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞丽奴小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.05,0:19:31.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞丽奴小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.96,0:19:35.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这招用起来果然辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.70,0:19:39.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.28,0:19:47.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,书？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.88,0:19:51.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里面写了什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.01,0:19:53.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是更大的藏宝地点吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.12,0:19:58.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全看不懂
